headline: Q3 Earnings Highlights: Textron (NYSE:TXT) Vs The Rest Of The Aerospace Stocks
summary: As the craze of earnings season draws to a close, here’s a look back at some of the most exciting (and some less so) results from Q3. Today, we are looking at aerospace stocks, starting with Textron (NYSE:TXT).
